<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1957-12-19T20:00:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1955-02-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="246" subtype="editorial-note" type="document" xml:id="d246">
                        <head>246. Editorial Note</head>
                        <p>On January 1, 1958, the treaties establishing a European Economic
                            Community (Common Market) and a European Atomic Energy Community (<gloss target="#t_EURATOM1">EURATOM</gloss>) officially entered into
                            force.</p>
